#: ../../source/language/javascript/engine.rst:2
msgid "引擎"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/engine.rst:5
msgid "V8"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/engine.rst:6
msgid "V8是Chrome的JavaScript语言处理程序（VM）。其引擎由TurboFan、Ignition和Liftoff组成。其中Turbofan是其优化编译器，Ignition则是其解释器，Liftoff是WebAssembly的代码生成器。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/engine.rst:9
msgid "SpiderMonkey"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/engine.rst:10
msgid "SpiderMonkey是Mozilla项目的一部分，是一个用 C/C++ 实现的JavaScript脚本引擎。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/engine.rst:13
msgid "JavaScriptCore"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/engine.rst:14
msgid "JavaScriptCore的优化执行分为四个部分，LLInt、Baseline、DFG、FTL。LLInt是最开始的解释执行部分，Baseline是暂时的JIT，DFG阶段开始做一定的优化，FTL阶段做了充分的优化。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/engine.rst:17
msgid "ChakraCore"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/engine.rst:18
msgid "ChakraCore是一个完整的JavaScript虚拟机，由微软实现，用于Edge浏览器以及IE的后期版本中。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/engine.rst:21
msgid "JScript"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/engine.rst:22
msgid "JScript是由微软开发的脚本语言，是微软对ECMAScript规范的实现，用于IE的早期版本中。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/engine.rst:25
msgid "JerryScript"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/engine.rst:26
msgid "JerryScript是一个适用于嵌入式设备的小型JavaScript引擎，由三星开发并维护。"
msgstr ""
